er hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/241/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Valaciclovir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Acyclovir, More', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, Rufinamide, More', 1767369485);
